</treatmentCitationGroup>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="DA1EFB74FFACFFA7FF236C5598B5F94F" blockId="30.[151,1436,1655,1752]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">
<emphasis id="E8D52766FFACFFA7FF236C559CF5F907" bold="true" box="[151,225,1655,1680]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Notes.</emphasis>
Our placement of this species is provisional. It is based only on the fact that it was described as a variety of 
<taxonomicName id="1DA180F7FFACFFA7FF236CBE9DB2F922" authorityName="Berlese" authorityYear="1920" box="[151,422,1692,1717]" class="Arachnida" family="Pachylaelapidae" genus="Pachylaelaps" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mesostigmata" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="squamifer">
<emphasis id="E8D52766FFACFFA7FF236CBE9DB2F922" box="[151,422,1692,1717]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Pachylaelaps squamifer</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, which we place in 
<taxonomicName id="1DA180F7FFACFFA7FD266CBE9808F922" authority="" authorityName="Masan" authorityYear="2007" box="[658,1052,1692,1717]" class="Arachnida" family="Pachylaelapidae" genus="Pachylaelaps" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mesostigmata" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Longipachylaelaps">
<emphasis id="E8D52766FFACFFA7FD266CBE9F3DF922" box="[658,809,1692,1717]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Pachylaelaps</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="E8D52766FFACFFA7FC886CBE9805F922" box="[828,1041,1692,1717]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Longipachylaelaps</emphasis>
)
</taxonomicName>
. The 
<typeStatus id="051A45D6FFACFFA7FBD46CBE9884F923" box="[1120,1168,1692,1716]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">type</typeStatus>
material of the species has been lost, and it is missing from the Berlese Acaroteca (
<bibRefCitation id="BE308685FFACFFA7FC816C9D9880F94F" author="Castagnoli &amp; Pegazzano" box="[821,1172,1727,1752]" firstAuthor="Castagnoli" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" refId="ref39579" refString="Castagnoli, M. &amp; Pegazzano, F. (1985) Catalogue of the Berlese Acaroteca. Istituto Sperimentale per la Zoologia Agraria, Firenze, Italy, 490 pp." type="book" year="1985">Castagnoli &amp; Pegazzano, 1985</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
